<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Murderous" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Murderous</orth> or <orth extent="full" opt="n">Murtherous</orth> (dissyll.; only once, <bibl n="shak. r3 4.1.56" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 1, 56</bibl>, trisyll. at the end of the line) committing murder, sanguinary: <bibl n="shak. luc 1735" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1735</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 9.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 9, 14</bibl> (<emph>m. shame</emph> == shameful murder). <bibl n="shak. r3 4.10.5" default="NO" valid="yes">10, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.129.3" default="NO" valid="yes">129, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.1.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 1, 159</bibl> (<emph>m. guilt</emph> == guilt of murder). <bibl n="shak. jn 4.2.255" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 2, 255</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.3.163" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 3, 163</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.49" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 49</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.49" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 49</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.185" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 185</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.2.193" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 2, 193</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.94" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 94</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.134" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 134</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.1.56" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.226" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 226</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.267" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 267</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.2.88" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 88</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 4.3.267" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. IV, 3, 267</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.147" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 147</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.336" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 2, 336</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 2.1.64" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 1, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.282" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 6, 282</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 5.1.61" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 1, 61</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.233" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 233</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.328" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 328</bibl> <emph>(m. to the senses).</emph>
